title: New Creator: Matt "Vanish Zito" Zito
body:
Name: Matt "Zito" Zito

Socials: https://twitter.com/ZitoFN_ 
https://www.twitch.tv/zitofn

Info: Vanish Zito is a professional Fortnite player and streamer. Averaging 300+ viewers per stream and with over 8,000 followers on Twitter, Zito engages with his fans through zone wars, competitive play, and community tournaments daily. 

Targeted Use Case: Twitter group chats and various engaging use cases. Pay out in his coin to tournament winners daily, integrating his coin in streams. 

Community Treasury Grant Tier: $500

A "Yes" vote would approve Matt Zito as a creator, and provide a $500 grant.

A "No" vote would reject Matt Zito from the platform.
author: 0xa1e4270381e381E75ef6e4dDa1a27337a4Be0939
